window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I grabbed the wrong bag at the airport carousel... and then made a deal with the devil from my darkest fantasies.</b></p> <p>Picked out a dress. Accepted his ring. Walked down the aisle under the watchful eyes of more killers than I can count. And became his wife.</p> <p>I resolved to keep my heart shut from him. Until this marriage of convenience took an unexpected turnâ€¦ And became something <i>very </i>real.</p> <p>Just as I started to believe in how real it was, he did something unforgivable.</p> <p>Something that reminded me of the kind of monster he was. Something that reminded me that I was a fool for trusting him. Something that reminded me that our world should've never crossed.</p> <p>It's too late now to back out now. Because as he promised me when he shackled me with the ring on his finger: He'll never let me go.</p> <p>Vengeful Promises <i>is a dark mafia romance featuring a marriage of convenience. It is book two of the Siderov Bratva duet, which must be listened to in order, beginning with </i>Vengeful Proposal. <i>For mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
